Package: easybio
Title: Single-Cell Annotation Using CellMark2 Database
Version: 1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Wei", "Cui", email = "m2c.w@outlook.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"))
Description: This package provides a comprehensive and user-friendly interface for single-cell annotation based on the CellMark2 database. This package streamlines the process of assigning biological labels to single cells, enhancing the analysis of single-cell RNA sequencing data. Features include efficient querying, integrated visualization. Ideal for researchers in the field of single-cell biology and transcriptomics.
URL: https://github.com/person-c/easybio
